{"tid":2051933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】許智峯私人檢控深水埗的士撞人案 裁判官受理下令涉案司機應訊","createTime":"2020-06-05T06:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T08:40:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4af3598db9e6c0e8ebb9d9477d1c2c3a73fa40","tid":2051933,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200605/2QJXQMB3NNPUOZA4S2ZRSIICJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F2QJXQMB3NNPUOZA4S2ZRSIICJI%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Eqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=084c97ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F2QJXQMB3NNPUOZA4S2ZRSIICJI%2F&h=7ee45d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200605/2QJXQMB3NNPUOZA4S2ZRSIICJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯早前就警員於西灣河向少年開槍一事，以及的士司機於深水埗開車撞入人群事件，分別向法庭提私人刑事檢控，法院今閉門處理許的兩宗申請。聆訊後許智峯透露，裁判官下令向涉案的士司機鄭國泉發出傳票，指示鄭須到庭應訊，是反修例運動以來首宗成功提出私人檢控的案件。"},{"pid":"4f31ead8cfec3211da295472d054b4cbccf187e5","tid":2051933,"uid":180168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"開槍嗰單呢?"},{"pid":"7b24b8f5b94f8d36ef0d67a342758067917d5245","tid":2051933,"uid":328890,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ecd9dc1d33b71ae7d38eae28d7e6d3500166fc0","tid":2051933,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f243a8db9148f53d31173da897fe641cac6b6a5","tid":2051933,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"檢控要民間自己，克服萬難先去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm